Titles.eng: Once in a Lifetime with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩と一期一会

Summaries.eng: Teaching Yuri how to play tennis is harder than herding cats.
Summaries.jpn: 亀井戸高校のテニスコートに立つ、ユリとかなえ。テニス部らしく、ちゃんとテニスの練習をしたいユリとは裏腹に、かなえはおかしな構えや動きを次々繰り出していき…。

Titles.jpn: 先輩とカリビアン

Summaries.eng: Takamiya Nasuna has returned to play tennis, but first they have to harvest the court.
Summaries.jpn: 海外に行っていた“なすの”が、日本へ帰ってきた！ なすのを交えて、久々に3人で練習することになったテニス部。だが、かなえの暴走で、またも真面目な部活とは程遠い雰囲気に？？

Titles.jpn: 先輩と黄金狂時代

Summaries.eng: Bando Marimo means well, but she has a soul of an old man... a perverted old man.
Summaries.jpn: 元気でキレイで優しくて、でも変態なテニス部員“まりも”。パンツをかぶっているところをユリに見つかって、一度は反省したかと思いきや、まりもの変態ぷりは更にエスカレートしていき…。

Titles.jpn: 先輩とグーニーズ

Summaries.eng: Kanae has invited the club to her house... things get awkward from here.
Summaries.jpn: テニス部のメンバーで、かなえの家へ遊びに行くことに。でも、不気味な玄関マットや壁のシミ、そしてクローゼットの中身まで…。この家は、みんなどこか変！？

Titles.jpn: 先輩とDENGEKI

Summaries.eng: All jokes aside, Nasuno decides to get serious and play at her full strength!
Summaries.jpn: 真面目にテニスの練習をする気配がない先輩たちへ、思わず「ヘタクソ」と言ってしまうユリ。それを聞いたなすのは、ユリにテニス対決を持ちかける。

Titles.jpn: 先輩とウォーターワールド

Summaries.eng: The girls enjoy a day at the pool by themselves.
Summaries.jpn: 亀井戸の街に大型プールが完成し、早速行ってみることにしたテニス部の4人。貸し切り状態のプールで、先輩たちの暴走が今、始まる…。

Titles.eng: From Russia with Love with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とロシアより愛をこめて

Summaries.eng: The Club needs new members!
Summaries.jpn: テニス部へ新入部員を勧誘するため、“対策会議”が開かれた。見当違いな勧誘プランを提案する先輩たちに、呆れかえるユリ。しかし、そんなユリの胸の内には、ある想いがあった。

Titles.eng: Born on the Fourth of July with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩と7月4日に生まれて

Summaries.eng: Nasuno wants to create something "special" for her father's birthday.
Summaries.jpn: もうすぐ、なすののお父さんの誕生日！プレゼントに悩むなすのへ、ユリは「手作りのものにしては？」と提案する。かくしてなすのは、お菓子作りへ挑戦することに。

Titles.jpn: 先輩とディナーラッシュ

Summaries.eng: Marimo gets a... job?
Summaries.jpn: 豚丼屋でアルバイトを始めることになったまりも。仕事を覚えない新人バイトに困りながらも、一生懸命指導する店長。だが、まりもの暴走で、店内は大変な騒ぎに！？

Titles.jpn: 先輩とウハウハザブーン

Summaries.eng: The showers at school are broken so the club visit the public baths.
Summaries.jpn: テニス部なのに、なぜかサッカーの練習を頑張り過ぎたせいで、汗臭くなったかなえたち。まりもの提案で急遽、銭湯へ行くことになり、女の子だけで裸の付き合いが・・・。

Titles.jpn: 先輩とナチョ・リブレ

Summaries.eng: Let's go to a festival!
Summaries.jpn: ゆかたを着て、みんなでお祭りへGO！ 「輪投げ」や「ヨーヨー釣り」など、露店を堪能するユリとかなえたち。だがそこへ突如、謎の人物が!?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とシックスセンス

Summaries.eng: The club is finally back to practicing but when they lose their only ball...
Summaries.jpn: テニスコートを飛び出したボールを追って、旧校舎へ迷い込んだ4人。やがてそこが心霊スポットだと気付くが、ボールを求め、探索を決意する。

Titles.jpn: 先輩とフルメタルジャケット

Summaries.eng: The four members of tennis club are asked to help with a bean throwing event by Kanae's cousin, who works at a nursery school. Concerned the children are frightened of her, Marimo receives advice from the principal, but...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とワンス・アンド・フォーエバー

Summaries.eng: Kondo-san from the newspaper clubs asks to interview the tennis club. Can the excited upperclassmen properly show off the activities of the tennis club?!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とトランスフォーマー

Summaries.eng: At Nasuno's suggestion, the four girls go on an overnight trip together. However, as expected, there's something strange about the method of transportation and lodging arranged by Nasuno...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とピンポン

Summaries.eng: After finishing practice on their overnight trip and recharging themselves in the bath, the four girls hold a hot springs table tennis tournament. How will the gradually escalating battle end?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とマーズ・アタック

Summaries.eng: On the final day of their trip, the tourist spot the manager told the girls about turns out to be a silver mine! And what event occurs on the bus on their way home...?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とエボリューション

Summaries.eng: When Nasuno suddenly declares she wants a pet, she and the other members head to the pet store where they find unbelievable animals!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とラン・ローラ・ラン

Summaries.eng: The day of the sports festival has arrived. Having entered a club relay race, the members come together to try to win, but...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とサイダーハウス・ルール

Summaries.eng: When Kanae becomes upset over her short stature, Nasuno takes her to a ranch. Will milking a cow make her taller!?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とメジャーリーグ

Summaries.eng: One day, the four girls take on the base ball club with their right to use the tennis court on the line. Certain character appears to fill their roster, turning it into a white hot battle!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とフィールド・オブ・ドリームス

Summaries.eng: At the bottom of the first inning with bases loaded and two outs, batter Kanae breaks out a certain pose! And finally, the conclusion!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とE.T.

Summaries.eng: One night, a mysterious flying object crash lands at Marimo's house. From the dazzlingly bright light appears an alien who calls himself "Tomalin!"

Titles.jpn: 先輩とおいしいレストラン

Summaries.eng: Kanae and Yuri go to an udon restaurant with coupons they received from Kondo-san. However, there's nothing ordinary about this udon restaurant!

Titles.eng: The World is Not Enough with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とワールド・イズ・ノット・イナフ

Summaries.eng: Nasuno-senpai takes everyone skiing. On what kind of course did the four skiing beginners end up?!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とスタンド・バイ・ミー

Summaries.eng: When it starts pouring rain, everyone seeks shelter at Kanae's house. On their way home, Kanae is struck by a bolt of lightning and uses her superpower "Kana Kana Wave"...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とマッドマックス

Summaries.eng: Nasuno is saved from a group of seemingly terrifying hooligans by a high school student named Yota. However, another group of assassins appears!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とシザーハンズ

Summaries.eng: At the suggestion of a long-haired Nasuno and short-haired Kanae, Yuri accompanies them to a salon. What NEW hairstyles does she see during her trip?!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とハングオーバー!

Summaries.eng: The group heads to the shrine for their first visit of the New Year. After drinking some amazake, Yuri runs out of control and things turn dire!?

Titles.jpn: 先輩と8マイル

Summaries.eng: Nasuno's bakery is 300 million yen in debt?! The girls try coming up with a new menu for the reconstruction of the store, but...

Titles.eng: The Merchant of Venice with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とヴェニスの商人

Summaries.eng: A story of Yuri as a third year middle school student. After making it into Kameido High School, Yuri tries to join the tennis team, but...

Titles.jpn: 先輩と羅生門

Summaries.eng: When Kanae's strings break the gang heads to a tennis supply store. The store stocks nothing but unusual strings. Which strings will Kanae choose?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とコンスタンティン

Summaries.eng: Yuri encounters the lingering spirit of her uncle at his funeral. Somehow her uncle takes control of her body, and...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とドリームキャッチャー

Summaries.eng: While Marimo is playing games at home, she is suddenly sucked into the game world through her TV. Will Marimo make it safely back to her own world?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とトゥモロー・ネバー・ダイ

Summaries.eng: The national tennis tournament has begun! What secret strategy does Kanae use against the formidable Usagikame High?!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とコーチ・カーター

Summaries.eng: The fearsome final exams are approaching. The girls gather at Kanae's house to study.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とメン・イン・ブラック

Summaries.eng: When Marimo forgets her lunch at home, her freeloading alien roommate Tomarin comes to deliver it. The girls decide to show Tomarin around Kameido High School, but for some reason school's a little unusual that day...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とロミオ・マスト・ダイ

Summaries.eng: For some reason Kanae receives aquarium tickets from a man riding an elephant. The girls decide to go together, but the situation at the aquarium becomes increasingly inappropriate...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とトレインスポッティング

Summaries.eng: Kondo-san of the school paper asks Yuri for help with investigating the legend of the cherry tree growing in the school yard. Apparently something strange happens to those who receive romantic confessions underneath the tree.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とランボー

Summaries.eng: Kanae and Yuri discuss watching the meteor show said to appear that night. They plan to gether on the roof of Nasuno's house, but... Will they be able to see the meteor shower?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とジョーズ

Summaries.eng: The swimsuit episode is finally here! Everyone is brimming with excitement as they enjoy the beach in a variety of ways, but...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とキャスト・アウェイ

Summaries.eng: Yuri panics as the previous episode requires a sequel. Though the girls end up adrift at sea, Yuri wonders if the relaxed upperclassmen truly are just brave.

Titles.eng: Enemy at the Gates with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とスターリングラード

Summaries.eng: Yuri is shown paranormal photos at Udonko's shop. She tries to welcome home Udonko's older sister and is shocked to learn she's the ghost she once met at a funeral.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とハムナプトラ

Summaries.eng: Kanae travels to her grandmother's home in the middle of the Egyptian desert to visit her grandfather's grave. It seems her extraordinary behavior comes from her grandmother.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とGOAL！

Summaries.eng: Yota practices to prepare for a practice soccer match. Nasuno offers to be his training partner, but she makes a ridiculous suggestion to help him win the game.

Titles.eng: Shaun of the Dead with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とショーン・オブ・ザ・デッド

Summaries.eng: Marimo and Tomarin walk through town in the blazing heat. Inside an air-conditioned electronics store, Marimo begins explaining human electronics to Tomarin, but...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とバグズ・ライフ

Summaries.eng: The girls are hanging out at a candy store in the middle of summer vacation. When Kanae suggests they do something special for summer vacation, they begin throwing around ideas.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とアポカリプト

Summaries.eng: Nasuno and Marimo have tea at a cafe. When Nasuno says she wants to work a part-time job to learn more about society, Marimo begins passionately offering advice based on her one day of work at a pork bowl restaurant!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とターミナル

Summaries.eng: The girls win tickets to a certain place is a shopping mall lottery. Their destination is overseas, and they begin preparing for their trip, but...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とキリング・フィールド

Summaries.eng: The girls arrive in Cambodia. They go on a conventional sightseeing tour, visiting ruins and more ruins in a tuk tuk.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とビューティフル・ドリーマー

Summaries.eng: Today is the cultural festival! Yuri's class is putting on a tuna dissection show. Yuri and Udonko begin crawling full speed ahead to check out the other class' attractions.

Titles.jpn: 先輩と猫の恩返し

Summaries.eng: After losing an obstacle course race in a sports festival long past, the tennis club is assigned to pick up garbage in the school's courtyard. Marimo comments on how ironic it is that society's garbage should have to pick up garbage, when...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とダイ・ハード3

Summaries.eng: The girls decide to hold a takoyaki party to celebrate fall. When they realize they have none of the necessary ingredients, they go to the store to buy some.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とエイリアンVSプレデター

Summaries.eng: Udonko decides to do a story on the mysterious alien Tomarin. The jokes fly during the interview due to their surprisingly good chemistry.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とレザボア・ドッグス

Summaries.eng: Kanae suddenly enters the classroom while spitting blood. Shocked and dismayed, Marimo cannot contain her anger when she sees her hurt friend. In her quest to avenger her friend, she becomes a goddess of revenge...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とミッション：インポッシブル

Summaries.eng: Kanae suddenly enters the classroom while spitting blood. The lead-in is the same until this point, but don't let that bother you. The girls decide to scout out a rival school, but...?

Titles.jpn: 先輩と賢者の石

Summaries.eng: The girls decide to roast potatoes. A certain fellow probably knows the most about sweets, but that aside, things don't generally go well for the girls as they can't find kindling and fail to start a fire properly...

Titles.eng: The Day After Tomorrow with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とデイ・アフター・トゥモロー

Summaries.eng: Seasons turn, and winter arrives. As Yuri walks through town in the brisk air, with a sidelong glance to Marimo slipping across frozen puddles, she spots Kanae wearing a mask for once.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とソーシャル・ネットワーク

Summaries.eng: This mallet and mortar have been passed down for generations.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とジョンQ

Summaries.eng: My grandma's in the hospital for Tommy John surgery.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とバックドラフト

Summaries.eng: The upperclassmen of the Tennis Club have PE class outside on a cold day. After warming up with exercise moves of their own creation, they take on the high jump.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とゴールデンアイ

Summaries.eng: Kanae needs a new phone, but the clerk at the store keeps offering her products that are definitely not phones. Will Kanae and Yuri leave the store with a phone that can actually make calls?

Titles.jpn: 先輩と武士の一分

Summaries.eng: With Valentine's Day just around the corner, Udonko and Yuri decide to make chocolate. However, it seems Udonko is very confused about what Valentine's Day and even chocolate are supposed to be.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とプレミアム・ラッシュ

Summaries.eng: The cherry blossoms are blooming, and the girls decide to go flower watching. When they arrive at the park, Yuri notices they've brought a few friends with them.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とトレマーズ

Summaries.eng: The earth moves...

Titles.jpn: 先輩とボウリング ・フォー・コロンバイン

Summaries.eng: Udonko begs Yuri and Kanae for help with her family's udon business. They agree to help make udon at the shop and are taught the ins and outs of udon by a very special teacher.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とダークナイト

Summaries.eng: When Mika tears her ACL, Bobby asks the girls to take her place in his annual hero show. Yuri is unsure, but the other members enthusiastically agree to do it.

Titles.jpn: 先輩と魔法にかけられて

Summaries.eng: Once upon a time, there was a girl named Cinderella who wanted nothing more than to attend the party at the castle. However, with 245 evil sisters intead of two, will she be able to attend the party and meet her prince?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とミート・ザ・ペアレンツ

Summaries.eng: The girls decide to form a band to get more out of their youth. However, the discussion quickly reaches an unusually serious level with tons of realistic terminology thrown around.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とウィンブルドン

Summaries.eng: The team's annual "Practice Super Seriously Day" has arrived. While the girls do indeed practice something that resembles tennis, it's still a far cry from "serious practice."

Titles.eng: Planet of the Apes with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩と猿の惑星

Summaries.eng: Marimo runs into Udonko, who is on her way to look for an unidentified flying object that crashed into a nearby park. While searching for the UFO, they meet up with Tomarin and Tanaka-san, who points them in the direction of some peculiar "playground equipment."

Titles.jpn: 先輩と2001年宇宙の旅

Summaries.eng: Marimo and her friends are trapped on an alien planet when their spaceship breaks down. While searching for the rubber band they need to repair their ship's engine, they come across a strange domed structure. When they open the door, they find a shocking surprise waiting for them.

Titles.jpn: 先輩と呪怨

Summaries.eng: Right off the bat, Kanae-senpai is slurping cup noodles at the bottom of a giant hole. In the heavily accented speech of a pioneer, she invites Yuri to climb down into the hole and help her dig...? The long-awaited seventh season has begun! We look forward to another great year of Tekyu!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とアイアンクラッド

Summaries.eng: Kanae's grandmother moves back to Japan from Egypt for no reason. Yuri is invited to help pick fruit. Grandma, fruit, help pick. Okay?!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とブロークバック・マウンテン

Summaries.eng: "Summer vacation is almost over," Kanae remarks during the introduction. Yuri snaps back precisely, "This anime's seasons are totally random." And that anime, Tekyu, is about to start again! Yahoooo!!!!

Titles.jpn: 先輩とデンジャラス・ビューティー

Summaries.eng: When Yuri and Marimo realize they're gaining weight, they decide to go on a diet. The naturally slim Kanae offers to coach them, but her advice is shaky at best. Will the girls be able to lose weight?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とテッド

Summaries.eng: Kanae and Marimo are hanging out at the park on a cold day. When a bear happens to wander by, they decide to question him about his hibernation habits, but the bear has some shocking answers for them.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とフューリー

Summaries.eng: One day at school, Yuri suddenly hears Udonko's voice in her mind. Using her newfound telepathic powers, Udonko suggests they go bowling. With the rest of the Tennis Club in tow, Udonko leads them to the bowling alley which turns out to be located somewhere familiar to the group.

Titles.eng: The Grand Budapest Hotel with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とグランド・ブダペスト・ホテル

Summaries.eng: When Kanae complains about the cafeteria's food, the new lunch lady challenges her to a school food showdown. Kanae accepts, but on the day of the event, she is sitting at the commentator's table, while participating in her place is an all too familiar face.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とベティ・サイズモア

Summaries.eng: When Yuri doesn't come to school one day, the third years ask Udonko where she is. When they learn she's home sick with a cold, they arrange a trip to visit her.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とエクソシスト

Summaries.eng: When Yuri runs into Annenkov, she gets dragged into a mixer with Annenkov and her friends. However, no one would have expected the kind of men who show up and the disaster that befalls her in the bathroom.

Titles.jpn: 先輩と桐島、部活やめるってよ

Summaries.eng: Yuri is shocked when the seniors of the tennis club suggest they practice with the tennis club of Usakame High, their rival school's team. Though their announcement initially brings tears of joys to her eyes, they're quickly replaced by her regular irritation when she realizes just how similar the two teams are.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とストレイト・ストーリー

Summaries.eng: The tennis club is going camping! With baseball equipment, gold-plated RV, and not a single member with a driver's license, the girls are ready to go.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とプライベート・ライアン

Summaries.eng: Kanae comes up with a brilliant new way for the girls to practice. Will their new practice methods enable them to finally compete in and win the national tournament?

Titles.eng: Lord of the Flies with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩と蝿の王

Summaries.eng: Kondo needs help coming up with a subject to write on for the national school newspaper contest. Will the girls be able to help her write a contest winning article?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とセブン

Summaries.eng: The girls are exhausted after another hard day of everything but practicing tennis. They decide to get ramen to fill their empty stomachs.

Titles.jpn: 先輩と28日後…

Summaries.eng: The girls are going to the beach... if they can even make it there. With so many problems plaguing their trip there, will there ever be a beach episode?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とタイタニック

Summaries.eng: The girls are enjoying themselves at the beach when calamity strikes. Is this the end of the Kameido tennis club?

Titles.eng: The Super-Scary Super-Strange Files! Scariest Movie Ever with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩と戦慄怪奇ファイル コワすぎ!史上最恐の劇場版

Summaries.eng: After a day at the beach, the girls head to an inn to spend the night. However, there is a foreboding air about the shadow looking in...

Titles.eng: Night at the Museum with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とナイトミュージアム

Summaries.eng: The girls are bored at school when Nasuno announces that she bought an art museum. They immediately head there to check out the art, but the objects on display aren't what they were expecting.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とオブリビオン

Summaries.eng: The girls decide to have some fun playing an online RPG. Will their party amass a wealth of equipment and experience points or end in tragedy?

Titles.jpn: 先輩とフェイス/オフ

Summaries.eng: Yuri wakes up one morning to discover she's inside Marimo's body. But when she gets to school, she finds another version of herself inside her own body. Who is who? Who is the real Yuri?

Titles.eng: Once Upon a Time in America with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とワンス・アポン・ア・タイム・イン・アメリカ

Summaries.eng: It's Kanae's first year of high school. Discover the exciting adventure that led her and Nasuno to join the tennis club.

Titles.eng: Once Upon a Time in China with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とワンス・アポン・ア・タイム・イン・チャイナ

Summaries.eng: The upperclassmen's flashback continues. With Kanae and Nasuno already on the team, next to join them is...

Titles.eng: Enemy of the State with Senpai
Titles.jpn: 先輩とエネミー・オブ・アメリカ

Summaries.eng: It's the day of the Kameido High Marathon and the tennis club is raring to go. When Kanae and Marimo show up with strangely muscular bodies, it's only the beginning of a typically atypical race.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とサタデー・ナイト・フィーバー

Summaries.eng: The girls discover their tennis net is ripped, but all the club's funds have been spent on sandbags. With no other choice, they decide to work for a day at a fried chicken restaurant, where they run into a shockingly unfamiliar face.

Titles.jpn: 先輩とスピーシーズ
先輩とホームアローン
先輩とピッチ・パーフェクト
先輩と300
先輩と101
